Laila Fawzi (1923 - Jenụwarị 12, 2005), nke a na-akpọkwa Leila Fawzi na Layla Fawzy, bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri na onye nlereanya
Ọ bụ otu n'ime ndị ọsụ ụzọ nke ihe nkiri Ijipt ma mee ihe nkiri ihe karịrị iri asatọ na ise n'oge ọrụ ya
N'afọ 1940, e kpunyere okpueze nke Miss Egypt.
A mụrụ Fawzi na Turkey nye nne na nna ndị Ijipt
Nna ya nwere ụlọ ahịa akwa na Cairo, Damascus na Istanbul
Ọ meriri asọmpi Miss Egypt na 1940, e nyere ya obere ọrụ na ihe nkiri Egypt Wives Factory na 1941.
Ọ lụrụ di ugboro atọ; nke mbụ ya bụ onye Egypt na-eme ihe nkiri Aziz Osman, Anwar Wagdi sochiri ya, na Galal Moawad.
